comment._content: Princess Frederica of Hanover, (9 January 1848 – 16 October 1926) was a member of the House of Hanover. After her marriage, she lived mostly in England, where she was a prominent member of Society. en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Princess_Frederica_of_Hanover [http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/4058466892/] [http://www.flickr.com/photos/library_of_congress/5375080325/]
